---
description: Revenue pipeline + compliance guardrails
globs: apps/api/**,apps/web/**,packages/shared/**
---

- Onboarding flows must be idempotent and support retry without duplicate tenant/user creation.
- Starter/free plans must enforce appraisal quota limits server-side (never client-only).
- Referral codes must be stored as hashes only.
- Provisioning and critical mutations must emit `AuditLog` rows.
- Pilot funnel endpoints must validate with Zod and avoid exposing secrets in responses.
- AI insights must include versioned outputs with cost/inference caps and audit logs.
- Growth claims/referral credits must be idempotent and tenant-scoped.
